Subject: RE: cd player installation

I used heavy duty wire snippers and snipped a 1/4 inch or so into each
corner of the original space for the stereo. Then with pliers carefully bent
along the line. This way if I get the original stereo and want to put it
back I just bend them back up and it is perfect.

